{"title":"陕北腰鼓","authors":["李舟"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":1,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"陕北腰鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳起黄土高原的舞蹈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂起显示力量的腰鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个粗犷的汉子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只只小麦小米养育的腰鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根鼓槌，一条腰带，一片毛巾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是浓郁的风情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河的白杨是你们美丽的舞蹈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山丹丹花的高原争相吐艳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲击鼓面敲击闪光的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红高粱摇曳的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着高昂豪迈的节奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋转成一种民族气魄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扭动黄水的腰肢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪动黄土的皮肤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝着浓烈的谷酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是华夏的骨骼脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听，那首醇芳的民歌光华四溢"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}